board.name: te0712_200_2i
board.display_name: Artix-7 TE0712_200_2I. SPRT PCB: REV02, REV01
board.description: Artix-7 TE0712_200_2I Board (form factor 4x5cm) with 1GB DDR3, 100MBit Ethernet, speed grade -2 and industrial temperature grade. Supported PCB Revisions: REV02, REV01.

interface.name: DDR3_SDRAM
interface.description: DDR3 board interface, it can use MIG IP for connection.

interface.name: ETH0_RMII
interface.description: Primary interface to communicate with ethernet phy in MII mode.

interface.name: ETH0_MDIO_IO
interface.description: Secondary interface to communicate with ethernet phy when mode is selected as MII,GMII,1000BaseX.

interface.name: ETH0_MDIO_MDC
interface.description: Secondary interface to communicate with ethernet phy when mode is selected as SGMII.

component.name: asio
component.description: All Module B2B as single ASIO GPIO Port

component.name: uart0
component.description: USB-to-UART Bridge, which allows a connection to a host computer with a USB port

component.name: spi_flash
component.description: 32 MByte storage that can be used for configuration or data storage

component.name: sys_diff_clock
component.description: differential 50 MHz oscillator used as system differential clock on the board
